These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, action, satire, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, blues, rock, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, malaysian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, taxi, scooter
1. the indian is the fan of soul##1
2. the malaysian is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching crime movies##2
3. the indian is the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the person driving the taxi is the person watching satire movies##1
7. the fan of blues is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the pakistani is on the far right##1
9. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | crime   | drama  | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | soul    | folk      | rock    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indian | malaysian | pakistani |
| Transport     | scooter  | train       | snowmobile    | taxi     |

