.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, gardening, traveling, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, animation, epic, drama
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, mouse, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, cycling, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person watching drama movies is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the goat##2
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
8. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
9. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | gardening    | traveling  | video-games    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | animation  | drama  | epic |
| Pet           | goat      | mouse       | fish      | hedgehog       |
| Sport         | golf    | soccer | cycling | climbing |

