.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, garlic, plum, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, magic-tricks, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, journalist, project-manager, entrepreneur
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, airplane, boat
1. the project-manager is the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the journalist is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
8. the person eating tomato is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person eating plum and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | garlic | plum     | tomato   | spinach     |
| Hobby       | drawing   | skydiving   | magic-tricks | puzzles |
| Job         | mechanic   | project-manager | entrepreneur       | journalist    |
| Transport   | airplane    | train | skateboard  | boat    |

