.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant, manager, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, crime, drama
4 different pets are kept: snake, cat, guinea-pig, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, basketball, skiing
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is the freelancer##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is the owner of the cat##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is the manager##1
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the accountant is between the owner of the snake and the writer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | freelancer  | writer | accountant     | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | western  | crime | spy       |
| Pet           | cat       | mouse    | guinea-pig      | snake           |
| Sport         | lacrosse | badminton   | skiing   | basketball         |

