The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, designer, paramedic, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, sports, horror, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, climbing, water-polo
 1. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
 3. the paramedic is the person eating lettuce##1
 4. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating kale is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the chef is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 8. the designer is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person eating kale is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
10. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | lettuce         | kale         | apricot     | radish      |
| Job           | paramedic | chef | teacher    | designer     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | horror       | documentary    | sports       |
