3. the russian is between the person who's sport is baseball and the german##2
4. the software-developer is on the left of the german##1
5. the russian is the russian##1
6. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the german is on the left of the writer##1
8. the fan of country is on the far right##1
9. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | software-developer | musician | writer  | teacher |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | dubstep       | r&b     | country      |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | german      | russian   | indonesian   |
| Sport         | water-polo   | skateboarding    | rugby | baseball   |

