4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching epic movies##2
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
