 6. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
 7. the journalist is on the left of the videographer##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
 9. the firefighter is between the dancer and the person who's sport is badminton##2
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | nectarine        | mango    | eggplant | asparagus   |
| Job           | dancer | firefighter | journalist   | videographer |
