 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person eating pear is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person eating pear and the person eating broccoli##2
 9. the person eating radish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person eating pear and the person eating broccoli##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | 7up    | almond-milk    | soy-milk      | cola |
