 3. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the horse##2
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is the person eating pumpkin##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the horse is the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
